subject: Golf
Lightning
lead_paragraph: A beachside guest house owned by Tiger Woods was destroyed by fire yesterday. No one was in the house, which is in Jupiter Island on Florida’s east coast. A fire official said the fire was caused by lightning. Woods’s residence is near Orlando.
